hadiths[36]{hadithnumber,text}:
452,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam (hujrey sey nikal kar) hamarey paas aaye aur farmaya : ''Allah taala ney tumharey liye eik aisi namaz ka izafa kiya hai padhi. , jo tumharey liye surkh oonton sey behtar hai, wo witr hai, Allah ney uska waqt tumharey liye namaze Isha sey ley kar Fajr key tulu honey tak rakha hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Khaarija bin Huzaafa ki hadees gharib hai, isey hum sirf Yazeed bin abi Habib hi ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 2- baaz muhaddeseen ko is hadees mein weham huwa hai. unhoney Abdullah bin Rashid Zarqi kaha hai, ye weham hai (sahih (Zufi) hai) padhi. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera , Abdullah bin Amr , Barida , aur abu Basra Ghifaari (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 4- Abu Basra Ghifaari ka naam Hameel bin Basra hai, aur baaz logon ney Jameel bin Basra kaha hai, lekin ye sahih nahin, aur Abu Basra Ghifaari eik doosrey shakhs hain jo Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat kartey hain aur wo Abu-Zar key bhatijey hain."
453,"Witr tumhari farz namaz ki tarah lazimi nahin hai, balke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney isey sunnat qarar diya aur farmaya : Allah witr (taaq) padhi. hai aur witr ko pasand karta hai, aey ehale-Quran ! tum witr padha karo. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar , ibne-Masood aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
454,"Witr lazim nahin hai jaisa ke farz namaz ka maamla hai, balke ye Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki sunnat hai, isey Sufiyan Sory waghera ney ba-tareeq (Ubai Is-haq an Aasim bin Hamzaa an Ali) riwayat kiya hai padhi. aur ye riwayat Abu-Bakar bin Ayash ki riwayat sey ziyada sahih hai aur isey Mansoor bin Moa'tamir ney bhi Abu-Is'haq sey Abu-Bakar bin Ayash hi ki tarah riwayat kiya hai."
455,"Mujhey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hukm diya ke main witr soney sey pehley padh liya karun. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai, padhi. 3- Sahaba kiram aur unke baad ke logon mein sey ehle-ilm ki eik jamaat ney isi ko ikhtiyar kiya hai ke aadmi jab tak witr na padh ley na soey."
456,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tum mein sey jisey andesha ho ke wo raat key aakhiri pahar mein nahin uth sakeyga, to wo raat key shuru main hi witr padh ley. aur jo raat ke aakhiri hissey mein uthney ki ummid rakhta ho to wo raat ke aakhiri hissey mein witr padhey, kyonkey raat ke aakhiri hissey mein Quran padhney par farishtey hazir hotey hain, ye afzal waqt hai.''"
457,"Unhoney Ummul-momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ke witr ke barey mein puchha , to unhoney kaha : aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney raat ke har hissey mein witr padhe hai. shuru raat mein bhi darmiyan mein bhi aur aakhiri hissey mein bhi. aur jis waqt aap ki wafat hui to aap ka witr sahar tak pahunch gaya tha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Ali , Jabir , abu-Masood Ansari aur abu-Qatada (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 4- baaz ehle-ilm ke nazdik yehi pasandida hai ke witr raat key aakhiri hissey mein padhi jaey."
458,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam witr tehra rakat padhtey they lekin jab aap umr raseeda aur kamzor ho gaey to saat rakat padhney lagey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Umme-Salma (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees Hasan hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey witr tehra , giyara , nau , saat , paanch , teen aur eik sab marvi (riwayat hui) hain. 4- Is-haq bin Ibrahim (ibne Raahviya) kehtey hain : ye jo riwayat hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam witr tehra rakat padhtey they, iska matlab ye hai ke aap tahajjud (qiyamul-lail) witr key sath tera rakat padhtey they, to is mein qiyamul-lail (tahajjud) ko bhi witr ka naam dey diya gaya hai, unhoney is silsiley mein Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey eik hadees bhi riwayat ki hai aur Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key farman ''aey ehale-Quran ! witr padha kar '' sey bhi daleel li hai. ibne Raahviya kehtey hain ke aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney is sey qiyamul-lail murad li hai, aur qiyamul-lail sirf Quran ke maan-ney walon par hai (na ke doosrey mazhabon walon par)."
459,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki qiyamul-lail (tahajjud)  tehra rakat hoti thi۔ in mein paanch rakatein witr ki hoti thin, in (paanch) mein aap sirf aakhiri rakat hi mein qa'ada kartey they, phir jab muazzan Azan deta to aap khadey ho jatey aur do halki rakatein padhtey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein abu-Ayyub (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai, padhi. 3- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ka khayal hai ke (jis) witr ki paanch rakatein hain, un mein wo sirf aakhiri rakat mein qa'ada karega. 4- mainey is hadees ke barey mein ke ''Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam nau aur saat rakat witr padhtey they.'' Abu Musab Madeeni sey puchha ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam nau aur saat rakatein kaisey padhtey they? to unhoney kaha : aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam do-do rakat padhtey aur salam phertey jatey, phir eik rakat witr padh letey."
460,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam teen rakat witr padhtey they, in mein mufassal mein sey nau suraten padhtey har rakat mein teen teen suraten padhtey , aur sab sey aakhir mein « ‏قل هو الله أحد » padhtey they padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Imran bin Husain , ummul-momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) , ibne-Abbas , abu-Ayyub Ansari aur Abdur-Rehman bin Abzi (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. Abdur-Rehman bin Abzaa ney isey Ubai-bin Kaab sey riwayat ki hai. isi ke saath ye bhi marvi (riwayat hua) hai ke Abdur-Rehman bin Abzaa ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey (baraahe-raast) riwayat ki hai. isi tarah baaz logon ney riwayat ki hai, is mein unhoney (Abi) key wastey ka zikr nahin kiya hai. aur baaz ney (Abi) key wastey ka zikr kiya hai. 2- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey ehle-ilm ki eik jamaat ka khayal yehi hai ke aadmi witr teen rakat padhey. 3- Sufiyan Sory kehtey hain ke agar tum chaho to paanch rakat witr padho , aur chaho to teen rakat padho , aur chaho to sirf eik rakat padho. aur main teen rakat hi padhney ko mustahab samajhta hun. ibne-Mubarak aur ehle-Koofa ka yehi qol hai. 4- Muhammad bin Sirin kehtey hain ke log witr kabhi paanch rakat padhtey they, kabhi teen aur kabhi eik , wo har eik ko sahi samajhtey they."
461,"Mainey ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey puchha : kya main Fajr ki do rakat sunnat lambi padhun? to unhoney kaha : Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam tahajjud do do rakat padhtey they, aur witr eik rakat , aur Fajr ki do rakat sunnat padhtey ( goya ke) takbir aap key kanon mein ho rahi hoti. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Aaisha , Jabir , Fazal bin Abbas , abu-Ayyub Ansari aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- Sahaba aur Tabe-een mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, unka khayal hai ke aadmi do rakaaton aur teesri rakat key darmiyan (salam ke zariye) fasal (gap) karey, eik rakat sey witr karey. Malik , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya yehi kehtey hain."
462,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam witr mein « ‏سبح اسم ربك الأعلى » ، padhi. « ‏قل يا أيها الكافرون‏ » aur « ‏قل هو الله أحد » teeno ko eik eik rakat mein padhtey they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Ali , Aaisha aur Abdur-Rehman bin Abza (Raziallauh anhum) jinhon-ne Ubai-bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat ki hai, bhi hadeesen aai hain, aur isey Abdur-Rehman bin Abzaa sey baghair Abi key wastey sey baraahe-raast Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey bhi riwayat kiya jata hai. 2- Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey ye bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke aap witr mein teesri rakat mein muawwizatain aur « قل هو الله أحد » padhtey they, padhi. 3- Sahaba kiram aur unkey baad key logon mein sey aksar ehle-ilm ney jis baat ko pasand kiya hai, wo ye hai ke « ‏سبح اسم ربك الأعلى » ، padhi. « ‏قل يا أيها الكافرون‏ » aur « ‏قل هو الله أحد » teeno mein sey eik eik har rakat mein padhtey ."
463,"hamney Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey puchha : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam witr mein kya padhtey they? to unhoney kaha : pehli rakat mein (‏سبح اسم ربك الأعلى)doosri mein (قل يا أيها الكافرون)‏‏‏ aur teesri mein (‏قل هو الله أحد) aur muawwizatain padhi. padhtey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- ye abdul-Azeez Raavi asar Ata key shagrid ibne Juraij key walid hain, aur ibne Juraij ka naam Abdul-Malik bin Abdul-Azeez bin Juraij hai. 3- Yahya bin Saeed Ansari ney ye hadees b-tareeq : (Umra an Aaysha an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) riwayat ki hai."
464,"Mujhey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney ye kalimaat sikhaey jinhen main witr mein padha karun, wo kalimaat ye hain : (اللهم اهدني فيمن هديت وعافني فيمن عافيت وتولني فيمن توليت وبارك لي فيما أعطيت وقني شر ما قضيت فإنك تقضي wala يقضى عليك وإنه لا يذل من واليت تباركت ربنا وتعاليت) ''aey Allah ! mujhey hidayat dey kar un logon mein shamil farma jinhen tu ney hidayat sey nawaza hai, mujhey aafiyat dey kar un logon mein shamil farma jinhen tu ney aafiyat bakhshi hai, meri sarparasti farma kar , un logon mein shamil farma jin ki tu ney sarparasti ki hai, aur jo kuchh tu ney mujhey ata farmaya hai is mein barkat ata farma , aur jis shar ka tu ney faisla farma diya hai us sey mujhey mehfooz rakh , yaqinan faisla tu hi sadir (jaari) farmata hai, terey khilaf faisla sadir (jaari) nahin kiya ja sakta , aur jis ka to wali ho wo kabhi zaleel aur khuwar nahin ho sakta , aey hamarey rab ! to bahut barkat wala aur bahut buland aur baala hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, 2- isey hum sirf isi sanad sey yani Abul Horaa Sa'di ki riwayat sey jantey hain, inka naam Rabeea bin Sheban hai. 3- merey ilm mein witr key qunoot key silsiley mein is sey behtar koi aur chiz Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey marvi (riwayat hui) ho malum nahin. 4- is bab mein Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai, 5- ehle-ilm ka witr key qunoot mein ikhtilaf hai. Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ka khayal hai ke witr mein qunoot purey saal hai, aur unhoney rukoo sey pehley qunoot padhna pasand kiya hai, aur yehi baaz ehle-ilm ka qol hai Sufiyan Sory , ibne-Mubarak , Is-haq aur ehle-Koofa bhi yehi kehtey hain. 6- Ali bin abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke wo sirf Ramzan key nisf (aadha), aakhir mein qunoot padhtey they, aur rukoo key baad padhtey they. 7- baaz ehle-ilm isi taraf gaey hain, Shafai aur Ahmed bhi yehi kehtey hain."
465,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo witr padhey baghair so jaey, ya usey padhna bhool jaey to jab yad aaye ya jaagey padh ley.''"
466,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo witr padhey baghair so jaey, aur jab subah ko uthey to padh ley.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye pehli hadees sey ziyada sahih hai. 2- mainey abu-Daawood Sijzi yani Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Ash-as ko suna , wo keh rahey they ke mainey Ahmed bin Hanbal sey Abdur-Rehman bin Zaid bin Aslam key barey mein puchha to unhoney kaha : unke bhai Abdullah mein koi muzaaeqa (haraj) nahin. 3- mainey Muhammad ( Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ( ko zikr kartey suna , wo Ali bin Abdullah ( ibne-Madeeni ( sey riwayat kar rahey they ke unhoney Abdur-Rehman bin Zaid bin Aslam ko zaeef qarar diya hai aur kaha hai ke (un key bhai) Abdullah bin Zaid bin Aslam Suqa (bharosemand) hain, 4- koofa key baaz ehle-ilm isi hadees ki taraf gaey hain, wo kehtey hain ke aadmi witr padh ley jab usey yad aa jaey, chaahe suraj nikalney ke baad yad aaye. yehi Sufiyan Sory bhi kehtey hain."
467,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''subah honey sey pehley witr padh liya karo.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
468,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''subh honey sey pehley witr padh liya karo.''
469,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab Fajr tulu ho gaee to tahajjud (qiyamul-leil) aur witr ka sara waqt khatam ho gaya, lihaza Fajr key tulu honey sey pehley witr padh liya karo.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Musa in alfaz key sath munfarid (alag) hain, 2-  Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke aap ney farmaya : '' Fajr key baad witr nahin.''  3- bahut sey ehle-ilm ka yehi qol hai. aur Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi kehtey hain : ye log namaze Fajr key baad witr padhney ko durust nahin samajhtey."
470,"Mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna : ''eik raat mein do baar witr nahin.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- is shakhs key barey mein ehle-ilm mein ikhtilaf hai jo raat key shuru hissey mein witr padh leta ho phir raat key aakhiri hissey mein qiyamul-leil (tahajjud) ke liye uthta ho, to Sahaba kiram aur un ke baad ke logon mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ki raey witr ko tod deney ki hai, unka kehna hai ke wo is main eik rakat aur mila ley taake (wo juft (jode ki shakl mein) ho jaey) phir jitna chahey padhey aur namaz key aakhir mein witr padh ley. isliye ke eik raat mein do baar witr nahin, Is-haq bin Raahviya isi taraf gaey hain, padhi. 3- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ka kehna hai ke jab usney raat key shuru hissey mein witr padh li phir so gaya, phir raat key aakhiri mein bedaar huwa to wo jitni namaz chahey padhey , witr ko na todey balke witr ko uskey apney haal hi par rehney dey. Sufiyan Sory , Malik bin Anas , ibne-Mubarak , Shafai aur ehle-koofa aur Ahmed ka yehi qol hai. aur yehi ziyada sahih hai, isliye ke kaee dusri riwaayaton mein marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney witr ke baad namaz padhi hai."
471,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam witr ke baad do rakatein padhtey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : abu-Umama , Aaisha Raziallahu anhuma aur deegar kaee logon sey bhi Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi tarah marvi (riwayat hui) hai."
472,"Main eik safar mein ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma key sath chal raha tha, main un sey peechhey reh gaya, to unhoney puchha : tum kahan reh gaey they? mainey kaha : main witr padh raha tha, unhoney kaha : kya Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki zaat main tumharey liye namuna nahin? mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko to apni sawari hi par witr padhtey dekha hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm isi taraf gaey hain, unka khayal hai ke aadmi apni sawari par witr padh sakta hai. aur yehi Shafai , Ahmed , aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi kehtey hain, 4- aur baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain ke aadmi sawari par witr na padhey. jab wo witr ka irada karey to usey utar kar zamin par padhey. ye baaz ehle-koofa ka qol hai."
473,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney chaasht ki baara rakatein padhin, Allah uskey liye jannat mein soney ka eik mehal taamir farmaeyga.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Anas ki hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. 2- is bab mein Umme-Haani , abu-Huraira, Nuaim bin Hamaar , Abu-Zar , Aaisha , abu-Umama , Utba bin Abd Sulami , ibne-Abi Aufi , abu Saeed Khudri , Zaid bin Arqam aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
474,"Mujhey sirf Umme-Haani (Raziallahu Anha) ney khabar di ke unhoney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko chaasht ki namaz padhtey dekha hai, Umme-Haani (Raziallahu Anha) bayan karti hain ke Fateh Makka ke din Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam unke ghar mein dakhil huye to ghusl kiya aur aath rakatein padhin, mainey aap ko nahin dekha ke aap ney is sey bhi halki namaz kabhi padhi ho, albatta aap rukoo aur sajdey purey purey kar rahey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Ahmed bin Hanbal ki nazar mein is baab mein sab sey ziyada sahih Umme-Haani (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees hai."
475,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Allah Taala farmata hai : aey ibne-Adam! to din key shuru mein meri raza key liye chaar rakatein padha kar , main purey din tumharey liye kafi hunga ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
476,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jisney chaasht ki do rakaaton ki muhafizat ki, uskey gunah bakhsh diye jaeyngey, agar-che wo samandar key jhaag key barabar hon''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Wakee, Nazar bin Shumeil aur doosrey kaee aimma ney ye hadees Nahas bin qaham sey riwayat ki hai. aur hum Nahas ko sirf unki isi hadees sey jantey hain."
477,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam chaasht ki namaz padhtey they. yahan tak ke hum kehtey ke aap isey nahin chodengey, aur aap usey chhod detey yahan tak ke hum kehtey ke ab usey nahin padhengey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
478,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam suraj dhal janey key baad Zohar sey pehley chaar rakatein padhtey, aur farmatey : ''ye aisa waqt hai jis mein aasman key darwazey khol diye jatey hain aur main chahta hun ke mera nek amal is mein ooper chadhey''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abdullah bin Saaib (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Ali aur abu-Ayyub Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey marvi hai ke aap zawal key baad chaar rakatein padhtey aur unkey aakhir main hi salam phertey."
479,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisey Allah Taala sey koi zarurat ho ya bani Adam mein sey kisi sey koi kaam ho to pehley wo achchhi tarah wuzu karey, phir do rakatein ada karey, phir Allah ki hamd aur sanaa bayan karey aur Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam par namaz (durood) aur salam bhejey, phir kahe : (لا إله إلا الله الحليم الكريم سبحان الله رب العرش العظيم الحمد لله رب العالمين أسألك موجبات رحمتك وعزائم مغفرتك والغنيمة من كل بر والسلامة من كل إثم لا تدع لي ذنبا إلا غفرته wala هما إلا فرجته wala حاجة هي لك رضا إلا قضيتها يا أرحم الراحمين). ''Allah key siwa koi mabood bar-haq nahin, wo Haleem (brudbar (samajhdar)) hai, karim (buzurgi wala) hai, pak hai Allah jo arshe-azeem ka rab hai, tamam tareefen Allah key liye hain jo Rabbul Aalameen (sarey jahano ka paalanhaar) hai, main tujh se teri rehmat ko wajib karney wali chizon ka aur teri bakhshish ke yaqeeni honey ka sawal karta hun, aur har neki mein sey hissey paney ka aur har gunah sey salamti ka sawal karta hun, aey sabse ziyada raham karne wale ! to mera koi gunah baqi na chhod magar to usey bakhsh dey aur na koi gham chhod , magar to usey door farma dey aur na koi aisi zarurat chhod jis mein teri khushnoodi ho magar to usey puri farma dey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- iski sanad mein kalam hai. Faaid bin Abdur-Rehman ko hadees key silsiley mein zaeef qarar diya jata hai. aur Faaid hi Abul Warqa hain."
480,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam hamein har mamley mein istikhaara karna isi tarah sikhatey jaisey aap hamen Quran ki suraten sikhatey they. aap farmatey : ''tum mein sey koi shakhs jab kisi kaam ka irada karey to do rakat padhey, phir kahe : (اللهم إني أستخيرك بعلمك وأستقدرك بقدرتك وأسألك من فضلك العظيم فإنك تقدر wala أقدر وتعلم wala أعلم وأنت علام الغيوب اللهم إن كنت تعلم أن هذا الأمر خير لي في ديني ومعيشتي وعاقبة أمري أو قال في عاجل أمري) ya kahe : (فِي عَاجِلِ أَمْرِي وَآجِلِهِ فيسره لي ثم بارك لي فيه وإن كنت تعلم أن هذا الأمر شر لي في ديني ومعيشتي وعاقبة أمري) ya kahe :(في عاجل أمري وآجله فاصرفه عني واصرفني عنه واقدر لي الخير حيث كان ثم أرضني به) ''aey Allah ! main terey ilm ke zariey tujh sey bhalai talab karta hun, aur teri taqat ke zariey tujh sey taqat talab karta hun, aur tujh sey terey Fazal ka sawal karta hun, to qudrat rakhta hai aur main qudrat nahin rakhta , to ilm wala hai aur main la ilm hun, to tamam ghaibon ko khub jaan-ney wala hai, aey Allah agar to jaanta hai ke ye kaam merey haq mein, merey deen, meri rozi aur anjam ke aetbar sey (ya aap ney farmaya : ya meri duniya aur aakhirat ke lihaz sey) behtar hai, to isey to merey liye aasan bana dey aur mujhey is mein barkat ata farma, aur agar to janta hai ke ye kaam merey haq mein, merey Deen , meri rozi aur anjam ke aetbar sey ya farmaya meri duniya aur aakhirat key lihaz sey merey liye bura hai to isey to mujh sey pher dey aur mujhey is sey pher dey aur merey liye khair muqaddar farma dey wo jahan bhi ho, phir mujhey is par razi kar dey.'' aap ney farmaya : ''aur apni hajat ka naam ley.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai hum isey sirf Abdur-Rehman bin Abi Al Mawaali ki riwayat sey jantey hain, ye eik Madni Suqa (bharosemand) shaikh hain, in sey Sufiyan ney bhi eik hadees riwayat ki hai, aur Abdur-Rehman sey deegar kaee Aaimma ney bhi riwayat ki hai, yehi Abdur-Rehman bin Zaid bin Abi Al Mawaali hain. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin Masood aur Abu-Ayyub Ansari Raziallahu anhuma sey hadeesen aai hain."
481,"Umme Sulem (Raziallahu Anha) ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aa kar arz kya ke mujhey kuch aisey kalmaat sikha dijiye jinhen main namaz padhi. mein kaha karun, aap ney farmaya : '' das baar « الله أكبر » kaho , das baar « Subhanallah » kaho , das baar « الحمد لله » kaho , phir jo chaho maango , wo ( Allah (har chiz par haan, haan kehta hai'' , ( yani qubul karta hai) . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abbas , Abdullah bin Amr , Fazal bin Abbas aur abu-Raafey (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- salaatul-tasbeeh key silsiley mein Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey aur bhi kaee hadisein marvi hain lekin koi ziyada sahih nahin hain, 4- ibne-Mubarak aur deegar kaee ehle-ilm salaatul-tasbeeh key qaail hain aur unhoney uski fazilat ka zikr kya hai, 5- abu Wahab Muhammad bin mazaaham Aamiri ney bayan kya ke mainey Abdullah bin Mubarak sey salaatul-tasbeeh key barey mein puchha ke jis mein tasbih padhi jati hai, to unhoney kaha : pehley takbir tahreema kahey, phir « سبحانك اللهم وبحمدك وتبارك اسمك وتعالى جدك wala إله غيرك » '' aey Allah ! teri zaat pak hai, aey Allah to har aeb aur har naqs sey pak hai sab taarifein terey hi liye hain, ba-barkat hai tera naam , buland hai teri shaan aur terey siwa koi mabood bar-haq nahin '' kahey, phir pandarah martaba سبحان الله والحمد لله wala إله إلا الله والله أكبر kahiye , phir «أعوذ بالله من الشيطان الرجيم » '' aur « بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم » kahey, phir Sura Fatiha aur koi Sura padhey , phir das martaba « سبحان الله والحمد لله wala إله إلا الله والله أكبر» kahey, phir rukoo mein jaey aur das martaba yehi kalmaat kahey, phir sar uthaey aur das martaba yehi kalmaat kahey, phir sajda karey das baar yehi kalmaat kahey phir sajdey sey apna sar uthaey aur das baar yehi kalmaat kahey, phir doosra sajda karey aur das baar yehi kalmaat kahey, is tarah sey wo chaaron rakatein padhey , to har rakat mein ye kul 75 tasbeehaat hongi . har rakat key shuru mein pandarah tasbeehein kaheyga, phir das das kaheyga, aur agar wo raat ko namaz padh raha ho to merey nazdik mustahab hai ke wo har do rakat key baad salam pherey aur agar din mein padhey to chahey to ( do rakat key baad) salam pherey aur chahey to na pherey . abu Wahab wahab bin Zamaa sey riwayat hai ke abdul-Azeez bin abi Razma kehtey hain ke Abdullah bin Mubarak ney kaha : rukoo mein pehley « subhana-rabbiyal-azeem » aur sajdey mein pehley « subhana-rabbiyal aala » teen teen baar kahey, phir tasbeehaat padhey . abdul-Azeez hi ibne-Abi Razma kehtey hain ke mainey Abdullah bin Mubarak sey puchha : agar us namaz mein saho ho jaey to kya wo sajda saho mein das das tasbeehein kaheyga? unhoney kaha : nahin ye sirf teen so tasbeehaat hain."
482,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney (apney chacha) Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey farmaya : ''aey chacha ! kya main aap key sath sila rehmi na karun, kya main aap ko na dun? kya main aap ko nafa na pahunchaaun? '' wo boley : kyon nahin, Allah key Rasool ! aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''aap chaar rakat namaz padhein, har rakat mein Sura Fatiha aur koi sura padhein, jab qirat puri ho jaey to (اللہ اکبر), (الحمد للہ), (سبحان اللہ) pandarah martaba rukoo karney sey pehley kahen, phir rukoo mein jaeyn to das martaba yehi kalimaat rukoo mein kahin , phir apna sar uthaeyn aur yehi kalimaat das martaba rukoo sey khadey ho kar kahen. phir sajdey mein jaeyn to yehi kalimaat das martaba kahen, phir sar uthaeyn to das martaba yehi kalimaat kahen. phir doosrey sajdey mein jaeyn to das martaba yehi kalimaat kahen, phir sajdey sey apna sar uthaeyn to khadey honey sey pehley das martaba yehi kalimaat kahen. isi tarah har rakat mein kahen, ye kul 75 kalimaat huye aur chaaron rakaaton mein teen sau (300) kalimaat huye. to agar aap ke gunah bahut ziyada ret waley badalon ke barabar bhi hongey to Allah Taala unhen maaf farma dega.'' to unhoney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! rozaana ye kalimaat kehney ki qudrat kis mein hai? aap ney farmaya : ''aap rozaana ye kalimaat nahin keh saktey to har Jume ko kahin aur agar har Jume ko bhi nahin keh saktey to har maah mein kahen.''  wo barabar yehi baat kehtey rahey yahan tak ke aap ney farmaya : ''to eik saal mein aap isey keh lein.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees abu-Raafey (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat sey gharib hai."
483,"hamney arz kya, Allah key Rasool! aap par salam bhejna to hamney jaan liya hai padhi. lekin aap par salaat ( durood ( bhejney ka tariqa kya hai? aap ney farmaya : ''kaho : اللهم صل على محمد وعلى آل محمد كما صليت على إبراهيم إنك حميد مجيد وبارك على محمد وعلى آل محمد كما باركت على إبراهيم إنك حميد مجيد'' aey Allah ! Muhammad aur aal Muhammad par rehmat nazil farma jaisa ke tu ney Ibrahim par rehmat nazil farmaai hai, yaqinan to Humed ( tareef key qabil) aur Majeed ( buzurgi wala ( hai, aur Muhammad aur aale-Muhammad par barkat nazil farma jaisa ke tu ney Ibrahim par barkat nazil farmaai hai, yaqinan to Humed ( tareef key qabil (aur Majeed (buzurgi wala) hai''. zyada ney b-tareeq Aamash an al-Hakam an Abdur-Rehman bin abi Leila eik zayed lafz ki riwayat ki hai ke unhoney kaha : aur hum ( durood mein) « وعلينا معهم » '' yani aur hamarey ooper bhi rehmat o barkat bhej '' bhi kehtey they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Kaab bin Ajra (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Ali , abu-Humed , abu-Masood , Talha , abu-Saeed , Barida , Zaid bin khaarija aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
484,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''qiyamat key din mujh sey logon mein sab sey ziyada qarib padhi. wo hoga jo mujh par sab sey ziyada salaat ( durood ( bhejeyga ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey ye bhi marvi hai ke aap ney farmaya '' jo mujh par eik baar salaat ( durood ( bhejta hai, Allah is par uskey badley das baar salaat ( durood ( bhejta hai padhi. , aur uskey liye das nekiyan likhi jati hain'' ( yehi hadees aagey aa rahi hai )"
485,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo mujh par eik baar salaat ( durood ( bhejeyga , Allah uskey badley is par das baar salaat ( durood ( bhejeyga ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abdur-Rehman bin Auf , Aamir bin Rabeea , Ammar , abu-Talha , Anas aur Ubai-bin Kaab (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- Sufiyan Sory aur deegar kaee ehle-ilm sey marvi hai ke rab key salaat ( durood ( sey murad uski rehmat hai aur farishton key salaat ( durood ( sey murad istighfar hai."
486,"dua aasman aur zamin key darmiyan ruki rehti hai, is mein sey zara si bhi ooper nahin jati jab tak ke tum apney Nabi karim Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam par salaat ( durood ( nahin bhej letey."
487,"hamarey bazar mein koi kharid o farokht na karey jab tak ke wo Deen mein khub samajh na paida kar ley. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- Alaa bin Abdur-Rehman bin Yaqub ye baap betey aur dada teeno taaba'ii hain, Alaa key dada aur Yaqub badey Tabe-een mein sey hain, unhoney umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ko paya hai aur un sey riwayat bhi ki hai."
